item.description:
There are two ways to create lists in YAML files, using newlines/dashes and using brackets/commas.
Lists Using Dashes ---- &#34;Apple&#34;- &#34;Banana&#34;- &#34;Green Bean&#34;- &#34;Pineapple&#34;- &#34;Grape&#34; Lists Using Brackets And Commas ---[&#34;Apple&#34;,&#34;Banana&#34;,&#34;Green Bean&#34;,&#34;Pineapple&#34;,&#34;Grape&#34;] Create Lists Within Lists Nested list item should be indented two spaces.
---- &#34;Apple&#34;:- &#34;Fuji&#34;- &#34;Granny&#34;- &#34;Green&#34;- &#34;Honeybrook&#34;- &#34;Banana&#34;- &#34;Green Bean&#34;- &#34;Pineapple&#34;- &#34;Grape&#34;
